<h1>Defense lawyers: Crew barely escaped stricken Sewol ferry</h1>
<!--endclickprintinclude--><!--startclickprintexclude-->
<!--no partner-->
<div class="cnn_stryathrtmp">
<div class="cnnByline">By <strong>K.J. Kwon</strong> and <strong><a href='https://twitter.com/madisoncnn' target='_blank'>Madison Park</a></strong><strong>, CNN</strong></div>
<div class="cnn_strytmstmp">updated 7:16 AM EDT, Tue June 17, 2014</div>
</div>
<!--google_ad_section_end-->
